headline: Adopt these habits to save energy and money this fall
summary: As fall brings cooler mornings and milder afternoon temperatures, it's the perfect time to revisit home energy habits and prepare for the winter heating season. Ameren encourages customers to actively monitor their energy usage – a routine that can help save money at home and work, and reduce strain on the grid.
